title: Leonard Cohen 21 May 1993
description:
Live Bootleg of Leonard Cohen from 21 May 1993

Taken from Boot Release &#039;First We Take Manhattan&#039;

Set List

1st set:
1. Dance Me To The End Of Love
2. The Future
3. Ain&#039;t No Cure For Love
4. Bird On The Wire
5. Everybody Knows
6. Anthem
7. One of Us Cannot Be Wrong
8. First We Take Manhattan

2nd set:
9. Avalanche - solo
10. Chelsea Hotel #2 - solo
11. Tower Of Song
12. Democracy
13. Waiting For The Miracle
14. I&#039;m Your Man
15. Joan Of Arc
16. Closing Time
17. Take This Waltz

Encores:
18. Sisters Of Mercy
19. Hallelujah
20. I Tried To Leave You
21. So Long, Marianne

Track 7 was omitted from original Broadcast so isn&#039;t present

&#039;Producers edited out accidental restart of Cohen&#039;s synthesizer on Tower of Song and all of One of Us Cannot Be Wrong.&#039;
